{"type": "article", "id": 33497, "title": "半透明的黑色“水箱”，是个能听又能看的音响｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-19T23:21:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34107, "name": "SIX"}, {"id": 34108, "name": "Eleven"}, {"id": 34113, "name": "SearchnDesign"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 6708, "name": "virgin"}, {"id": 18249, "name": "Arthur Xin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 166, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161019174735RQV0BZkrvgnP2WbY.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Rolling Workspaces by nendo</h3><p>          </p><p>为了即将在德国科隆举办的 <a href=\"http://www.orgatec.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ORGATEC</a> 办公家具展销会，日本品牌国誉（<a href=\"http://www.kokuyo.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">kokuyo</a>）与曾在 2014 年合作过的知名设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 再度联手，以办公室中常见的白板为核心设计了今年的展台 <a href=\"http://www.kokuyo.com/en/corporateprofile/news/2016101701.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rolling Workspace</a>。方形的白板被设计成了圆形，使它能够出现在各种平时意想不到的位置。与之配套的办公桌和长椅上都设计了凹槽，刚好可以把圆板固定在上面当作屏风。这么一个充满了旋转元素的办公室，是不是能激发人们的创意呢？</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019175833UVYrvWZ1IQ9X2iCJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019175833bxmYV2WIfNrBp0Qj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019175833IoSwDhMzULxCeHGy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019175833kcwVz6S0CGAJm7Pq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019175833yS2fwjqlG9bD5irP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019175833M4F8wzCUKQrqmLO0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lyric Speaker by SIX</h3><p>          </p><p>日本创意机构 <a href=\"http://sixinc.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SIX</a> 最近带来了一款相当惊艳的 Lyric Speaker 可视化音响，正如名字所指的那样，在播放音乐时它能够在半透明的 LCD 屏上同步显示歌词。这台音响通过蓝牙与手机连接后，还会根据音乐节奏变化歌词的显示方式。它所使用的歌词服务来自日本国内最大的歌词数据库，含有超过 120 万首的日文和英文歌词。最近 Lyric Speaker 还被日本的 Good Design Award 评选为本年度的百佳设计之一。美中不足的是，由于数据库的地域限制，这台音响只能在日本使用。如果你对它感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://lyric-speaker.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>了解更多的信息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610191745478uQCSR5b13YdZgit.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019174547sgHmd2FUAfa8txkv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019174547cWCz27ITRf4twLUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779951\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610191745478okZKRbM7FmBwLNg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019174547gZfGYDhnHemECWjs.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625917\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MAG-LEV Audio by MAG-LEV Audio team</h3><p>          </p><p>最近来自斯洛文尼亚的设计团队推出了全球第一款拥有悬浮转盘的唱片机 <a href=\"https://maglevaudio.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">MAG-LEV Audio</a>，能够悬浮在半空中的转盘用零重力的神奇体验为现今的唱片机设计拓展了一种新的可能。富有未来感的外观搭配播放时底座亮起的一圈橙色灯光，让转盘悬浮的视觉效果显得更加时尚。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/245727224/mag-lev-audio-the-first-levitating-turntable\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 880 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019200026HXcpvMZtzOUJo3e5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019200027xzi4YgP6TvuyKLDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019200026JQrVGU285sWIYRMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019200027VfSgK90q2tROLnCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019200027pCjhVnRevKud5g1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Virgin America First Class Shoe by Eleven</h3><p>          </p><p class=\"\">在研发智能运动鞋这件事上，一家航空公司的参与会带来怎样的惊喜？最近，美国维珍航空（Virgin America）就委托创意机构 &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.eleveninc.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eleven</a> 和运动鞋设计公司&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.searchndesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SearchnDesign</a>&nbsp;以头等舱为主题设计了这款名叫 First Class 的运动鞋，模仿安全带搭扣的鞋带设计相当醒目。鞋子采用来自意大利的皮革手工制作而成，不仅配备了一块 LED 屏幕，还具备 USB 充电端口以及 Wi-Fi 热点功能。融合了大量高科技的这款球鞋全球限量一双，<a href=\"http://www.ebay.com/itm/The-Worlds-Only-Virgin-America-First-Class-Shoe-/191994804785\" rel=\"nofollow\">目前正在 eBay 上拍卖</a>，出价已经超过一万美元。此次拍卖所得将会捐给 <a href=\"https://soles4souls.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Soles4Souls</a>，这是一家专门在贫困地区分发衣物和鞋子的非盈利慈善机构。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019180836HNrBfpevnMjLFV5Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019180836oURLFCAyYVM76j15.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019180836iSj4Ko8fzbpIdqm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019180836X45M9KIyZ1Dmitje.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019180836vJUCZmlakHxyF2I8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ON/OFF Alarm Clock by Arthur Xin</h3><p>当闹钟简化成一个开关时会是什么样？这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.arthur-xin.com/product/onoff.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">ON/OFF</a> 的闹钟是中国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.arthur-xin.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Arthur Xin</a> 的一款概念设计作品，当你需要关上闹铃时只需要把显示时间的那端按下即可。特别的是，当你按下之后，时间就会在翘起的另一端显示，就好像是一个跷跷板。从 Xin 的设计图可以看到，这个闹钟的操作可以在手机上进行，并且自带夜灯模式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610191726021RlcN8X9krSICPt5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172602kMxfLnVUZH6JuBOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172602WfTZQMGe10jcS9R4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172602fyPT5saXC6oIijcQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172602mMxE9zwyb6VBX4Qh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172602OZVhzELtAGF6UxWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LEGO playbox shopping bag by Junho Lee &amp; Hyun Chul Choi</h3><p>我们曾在上月的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32577.html\">购物袋</a>推荐中介绍过关于 bagvertising 的概念，最近来自纽约设计学院（School of Visual Arts）的 <a href=\"http://www.junholee.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Junho Lee</a> 和 <a href=\"http://evanchoi.squarespace.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hyun Chul Choi</a> 为 LEGO 设计的这款购物袋就是一个典型的例子。全红色方形袋子表面印着具有立体视觉效果的圆点，模拟出了积木上的圆形凸起。袋子真正的提手设置在内侧，袋子边缘有两个 LEGO 经典的黄色积木手，刚好可以遮住一部分手臂。提着这个袋子走在路上，如果你的衣服刚好遮住你的手臂，相信会吸引到不少好奇的视线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172536OaS97NKijwxLhCkv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610191725339NqrEBIlG0mWcP76.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172533JmZ7rCHe2ljDNW1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696822\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019172533e1SWiUgA6xIOcaou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}